---
description: Frontend component rules
globs: ["src/components/**"]
---
- Komponenty: funkcionalni, TypeScript, named exports
- Jeden component = jedna slozka (index.tsx)
- Props: explicitni interface, destructured v parametrech
- State management: VYHRADNE pres useItinerary() hook
- Zadny primy localStorage pristup mimo state/storage.ts
- Mapy: react-leaflet 5 deklarativni API (MapContainer, Marker, Polyline, Popup)
- DnD: @dnd-kit (SortableContext, useSortable) - NIKDY react-beautiful-dnd
- Edge cases: vzdy res empty state, loading state, error state
- A11y: WCAG 2.2 AA - focus visible, keyboard nav, ARIA labels
